### Nile Bites API - Example Requests
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or any HTTP client

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

###

### Create Order
POST http://localhost:3000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_name": "Ahmed Hassan",
  "phone": "01234567890",
  "address": "15 Tahrir Square, Cairo",
  "items": [
    {
      "name": "Grilled Chicken",
      "price": 300,
      "quantity": 1
    },
    {
      "name": "Mango Juice",
      "price": 55,
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ],
  "total_price": 410
}

###

### Get All Orders
GET http://localhost:3000/api/orders

###

### Get Specific Order
GET http://localhost:3000/api/orders/1

###

### Update Order Status
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/orders/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "confirmed"
}

###

### Create Reservation
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_name": "Sara Mohamed",
  "phone": "01234567890",
  "number_of_people": 6
}

###

### Get All Reservations
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reservations

###

### Get Specific Reservation
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reservations/1

###

### Update Reservation Status
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/reservations/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "confirmed"
}

###

### Delete Reservation
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/reservations/1

###

### Send Contact Message
POST http://localhost:3000/api/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Omar Ali",
  "phone": "01234567890",
  "email": "omar.ali@example.com",
  "message": "The food was amazing! Will definitely order again. Keep up the great work!"
}

###

### Get All Contacts
GET http://localhost:3000/api/contacts

###

### Get Specific Contact
GET http://localhost:3000/api/contacts/1

###

### Delete Contact
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/contacts/1

